      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "MusicSystem will have list of songs, albums, Artists\n\nUser opens system\nSearches songs / artists / albums\nSystem returns matching songs\nUser selects a song\nSystem will play the song\nUser can:\nPause / Resume\nSkip\nAdd to playlist\nSystem tracks play history\n(Optional) Subscription check for premium features",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "MusicSystem will have list of songs, albums, Artists\n\nUser opens system\nSearches songs / artists / albums\nSystem returns matching songs\nUser selects a song\nSystem will play the song\nUser can:\nPause / Resume\nSkip\nAdd to playlist\nSystem tracks play history\n(Optional) Subscription check for premium features",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
