      "updated": 1777014512305,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "if we have 1000, 2000, 3000, 4000 what is the next we will say 5000, we haven't see this question\nbefore, then how we have answered?\n    using our analytical mind, we found a pattern that 1000 difference in all so we have given\n    next, we have used this principal to create our ChatGPT.",
      "fontSize": 20,
