      "text": "how this is creating token, on what basis it is creating token, this is a tokenization process, this\nis different for each model, different for ChatGpt. we have one tokenization app using that we can find\nwhich tokenization process is used.\nwe have tiktokenizer app, we can check for which model what is the token for chatgpt, \nHi, how are you -> 5 token and each token has corresponding number.\n\n    24860, 11, 2650, 527, 499\n\nthese token or numbers will go to Chatgpt\n\n",
