      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1777017444761,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "if we ask same question Hi How are you, GPT gives us different answer why?\n    it works on predictive fashion , first time it recognizes different pattern and next time it\n    recongnizes different patter.\n\n    1, 2, 4,\n    1, 2, 4, next can be 8 or 7\n\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "if we ask same question Hi How are you, GPT gives us different answer why?\n    it works on predictive fashion , first time it recognizes different pattern and next time it\n    recongnizes different patter.\n\n    1, 2, 4,\n    1, 2, 4, next can be 8 or 7\n\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
